---
description: Capacitor Android, native adapters, and mobile build requirements
globs: ["android/**/*", "capacitor.config.ts", "src/capacitor.ts", "src/mobileArchitecture.ts", "src/mobileArchitecture.test.ts"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Production APK requires real `VITE_API_BASE_URL` (public HTTPS Worker); no placeholder URLs.
- Android cannot use WebView-relative `/api`; see `src/data/apiConfig.ts` validation.
- Respect safe areas, Android Back (nested Friends/Groups), and lifecycle persistence.
- External links via Capacitor Browser; preserve offline and reconnect behaviour.
- Logout and guest flows must survive WebView restart (`src/logout.ts`, signed-out marker).
- Build path: `npm run android:build` or `npm run android:build:verify`.
- APK output: `android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk`.
- Physical-device checks are separate from emulator and browser verification.
